    {
      "instruction": "<p>Cut your <strong>lemon[s]</strong> in half</p><p>Add the <strong>chopped cucumber</strong> and <strong>tomato</strong> to a bowl with a generous drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong>, a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and the juice of <strong>half</strong> the <strong>lemon[s]</strong></p><p>Give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>cucumber & tomato salad</strong></p>",
