      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>harissa & honey salmon</strong> over the <strong>couscous</strong> with the<strong> cucumber & tomato salad</strong> to the side</p><p>Spoon any <strong>remaining harissa & honey sauce</strong> from the pan over the salmon and garnish with a <strong>lemon wedge</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
